body:
You are receiving this email from the Stonebranch Universal Controller running in the ${ops_system_identifier} environment.

The purpose of this message is to inform you that a task has a status which may indicate that it requires attention.

Please use the following link to view the task (requires login):
${UAC_URL}?action=open&type=exec&id=${ops_task_id}

Alert generated on: ${_date('yyyy-MM-dd')} at ${_date('HH:mm:ss')} in time zone: ${ops_task_time_zone}

Task Type: ${ops_task_type}

Task name: ${ops_task_name}

Workflow to which the task belongs (if it exists): ${ops_workflow_name}

Top-level parent workflow: ${ops_top_level_workflow_name}

Task Launched at ${ops_launch_time}

Task Started at  ${ops_start_time}

Task Ended at    ${ops_end_time}

Status: ${ops_status}

Status Description: ${ops_status_description}

Exit Code: ${ops_exit_code}

************************************

Here is the Standard Output (if available):
${_output('STDOUT')}

Here is the Standard Error (if available):
${_output('STDERR')}

************************************

Universal Controller URL: ${UAC_Controller_URL}

Built-in Variable Dump:
${_scope}
